<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 3 (Leon) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リオン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Leon</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スタン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stahn</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ふん。
最初から素直にホットドッグを
買ってくればいいものを</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hmph.
He should've just bought the
hotdog from the beginning.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いやー、普通嫌がるだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I meeean, normally he'd hate that, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Not sure about this one.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それにしてもそのホットドッグ
すげーうまそうだな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But either way, that hotdog
looks like it'd taste SO good!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>.........</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>怖い！　目が怖いよ、リオン！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Scary! Your eyes have a scary look in them, Leon!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ところで、
俺達いったいいつまで
こんな事続けていくんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>By the way,
how long are we supposed to keep doing this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>僕に聞くな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm not the one you should be asking!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
